OL,3,CMan arrested over disappearance and
OL,4,Cmurder of Lisa Dorrian
OL,6,FA man has been arrested by police
OL,7,Finvestigating the disappearance and
OL,8,Fmurder of Lisa Dorrian.
OL,10,FThe 25-year-old from Bangor, Co Down,
OL,11,Fwas last seen alive on February 27,
OL,12,F2005 after attending a party at
OL,13,FBallyhalbert Caravan Park.
OL,15,FDespite extensive searches in multiple
OL,16,Flocations and campaigning by her
OL,17,Ffamily, Ms Dorrian's body has never
OL,18,Fbeen found.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
