OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1772733968
OL,3,CMan arrested over disappearance and
OL,4,Cmurder of Lisa Dorrian
OL,6,FA 40-year-old man was arrested in
OL,7,FMillisle on Wednesday on suspicion of
OL,8,Fassisting offenders and withholding
OL,9,Finformation.
OL,11,FDetective Chief Inspector Kerrie
OL,12,FForeman said: "The arrest comes days
OL,13,Fafter the 21st anniversary of Lisa's
OL,14,Fdisappearance and murder.
OL,16,F"It's been 21 long and painful years
OL,17,Ffor Lisa's loving family. They have
OL,18,Fnever given up their search for
OL,19,Fanswers and justice and, likewise, our
OL,20,Fdetermination remains steadfast.
OL,26,@tD@OOUxD@AOU
