OL,3,CMan arrested over disappearance and
OL,4,Cmurder of Lisa Dorrian
OL,6,F"I would appeal to anyone with
OL,7,Finformation to contact us on 101."
OL,9,FA 40-year-old woman and a 42-year-old
OL,10,Fman who were arrested last Wednesday
OL,11,Fas part of the investigation were
OL,12,Freleased on bail pending further
OL,13,Fenquiries.
